{"tid":1791384,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[短文]夜媽媽聽到人嗌救命","createTime":"2019-12-20T18:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T10:24:46.000Z","uid":71283,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7fa17e0ef51d20a839ce5e810251b6d1ec1d29d1","tid":1791384,"uid":71283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T18:00:34.000Z","msg":"「救命！救命！救命呀&mdash;&mdash;」淒厲的呼喊聲倏地劃破本應寧靜的香城。我睡眼惺忪地從溫暖的床爬起來，亮起燈望向黑漆漆的街道。見到附近的高樓也逐漸亮起一盞盞燈，凌晨時份亮起萬家燈火，營造出一種詭異的美&mdash;&mdash;最美麗的畫面往往出現於意外中。<br />\n<br />\n呼喊聲持續不到一分鐘便戛然而止，整個屋邨明亮異常，卻靜得像身處真空空間。漸漸，一兩分鐘過去，屋邨回歸黑暗一片，彷彿呼喊聲從不曾出現。我也開始抵受不了冷空氣帶來的煎熬，爬回那溫暖的被窩，造個好夢去。"},{"pid":"92ef52c8a476a6ab9232b688fc033b9bc93aaed6","tid":1791384,"uid":71283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T18:01:00.000Z","msg":"第一次出文自推 1/10"},{"pid":"4aef5816bd2aa6cf47ef96a3464b5ace97bfce26","tid":1791384,"uid":71283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T18:01:16.000Z","msg":"第一次出文自推 2/10"},{"pid":"4cf60f61cac7cbd2b411db1147090e165ed4ddc2","tid":1791384,"uid":71283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T18:01:27.000Z","msg":"第一次出文自推 3/10"},{"pid":"f56b315e80e09855d2e5026fdac48996e7df52c8","tid":1791384,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T18:01:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7918a79fda7c238ce12dd1c7c74006e538d847f","tid":1791384,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T19:43:08.000Z","msg":"[推上熱門]1221 今日最新行動應變<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/apxGsrU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/apxGsrU</a>"},{"pid":"e3d02746f9f2a878c2bc917e5336c9b1ef15b9b9","tid":1791384,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T10:24:46.000Z","msg":"嘩，好短下"}]}